Class SetGraph

java.lang.Object
  java.util.AbstractCollection<org.openrdf.model.Statement>
      com.complexible.common.openrdf.SetGraph
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<org.openrdf.model.Statement>, java.util.Collection<org.openrdf.model.Statement>, org.openrdf.model.Graph
public final class SetGraph
extends java.util.AbstractCollection<org.openrdf.model.Statement>
implements org.openrdf.model.Graph

Implementation of the Sesame Graph interface which assumes Set semantics as opposed to GraphImpl which uses a LinkedList internally. This implementation also assumes the user cares about context in statements and thus uses ContextAwareValueFactory for creating values and statements.

0.5
